{"tid":1181540,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣會幻想自己自殺嘅情景然後覺得好抒壓","createTime":"2019-06-01T16:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T09:12:18.000Z","uid":224311,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b88eb080d3bbc32ac44c0196a734cb65c71d43e9","tid":1181540,"uid":224311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由中學起已經想死但係唔想父母白頭人送黑頭人先冇走到最後一步，然後幻想自己自殺就上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舒服過打飛機同捽碟"},{"pid":"ce90124867b6a1093bf41a7d12cfb7fe29d25abf","tid":1181540,"uid":101253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"雙性人？"},{"pid":"e3316b3f7f7ce2356010bc781e4e6f15debfe699","tid":1181540,"uid":251925,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"人遲早都係死<br />\n如果唔開心 繼續受苦 早d解脫都係好事"},{"pid":"9cd82fe3f6002578e83456c5f0cf5e297d5c3ef7","tid":1181540,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:03:56.000Z","msg":"我會"},{"pid":"526091022df446e99bfd9bb57fba3e5cdce8965b","tid":1181540,"uid":170978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"幻想只係幻想，所有野都係過去累積，繼續行落去，你會發掘更加多。加油！人生！"},{"pid":"d382151e568760085a5741a3f9da61ff035caaff","tid":1181540,"uid":198386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"幻想嘅死亡係無痛<br />\n明白你呢種逃避生存嘅自我安慰<br />\n唔評論呢種幻想係咪健康<br />\n做人的確無咩意思，反正就出左世<br />\n活得無畏、活得心安係一個目標<br />\n<br />\n實際嘅死亡係呼吸困難、器官衰竭，而自己意識感受到全身嘅痛苦，人地睇到你痛苦一秒，喺自己個微觀世界就係一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似無限loop咁，真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />望就望自己有福氣壽終正寢，希望樓主都係"},{"pid":"c6be23ac02a0d73ba2109555c3b36d09c2378549","tid":1181540,"uid":4273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>2